Package: tp7-mtp
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-usb, python3-gi, python3-pyudev, gir1.2-ayatanaappindicator3-0.1, jmtpfs, libusb-1.0-0
Maintainer: sparkyfen
Description: TP-7 MTP file transfer tool
 Switches a Teenage Engineering TP-7 tape recorder from MIDI mode
 to MTP mode for file transfer on Linux. Includes a system tray
 helper with auto-detection and a CLI tool.
